<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 25 May 2026 05:16:52 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a13db290a908</link><description>&lt;p&gt;天哪眯着眼睛&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="a brown and white tabby squints in a patch of sunlight " height="3004" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/cygnoir/6a13db290a908.jpg" width="3004"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://cygnoir.some.pics"&gt;@cygnoir&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 May 2026 05:16:52 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a13cfdcc2298</link><description>&lt;p&gt;😺&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt='A small Pennsylvania bike license plate that says "MEOW" on a bluish green bike with mud splattered all over.' height="2422" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/brie/6a13cfdcc2298.jpg" width="2268"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://brie.some.pics"&gt;@brie&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 May 2026 04:28:15 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a13cf0652437</link><description>&lt;p&gt;🚲 北海岸内陆小径，休伦县&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A bluish-green bike propped along a covered wooden bench along a rail trail with a wide view of partially flooded farmland in the distance." height="2268" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/brie/6a13cf0652437.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://brie.some.pics"&gt;@brie&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 May 2026 04:24:42 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a13ce2f25be7</link><description>&lt;p&gt;🚲 俄亥俄&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A photo of a bluish-green bike stopped along a bench at the base of a large tree on the side of a trail." height="2268" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/brie/6a13ce2f25be7.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://brie.some.pics"&gt;@brie&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 May 2026 04:21:07 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>忘带水跑变走</title><link>https://some.pics/6a133b9be6b44</link><description>&lt;p&gt;🏃🏻 没带水就出发了，因为只跑一个小时应该不需要。没想到啊，虽然不该太轻松，但路线还是绕远了一些。长话短说：我需要水。最后几公里走的多跑的少。🤷🏻‍♂️&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="🏃🏻 Zonder water vertrokken want voor een uurtje is dat toch niet nodig. Onverwacht, het moet maar zo plezant niet zijn, dat rondje toch wat groter gemaakt. Lang verhaal kort: ik had water nodig. De laatste kilometers meer gestapt dan gelopen. 🤷🏻‍♂️" height="1486" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/atog/6a133b9be6b44.jpg" width="1179"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://atog.some.pics"&gt;@atog&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 17:55:42 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>